  assistance with Self Service Password  Security Awareness Training  and support for personally owned computers  Location  C 11 B Barracks Hours Monday   Friday  0700 1300 hours and 1400 1600 hours  In addition to the Barracks Help Desk requests for assistance may also be sent to help vmi edu  If your request requires personal assistance  you will be directed to go to the Barracks Help Desk  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 